#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/quenoth/Youth.cfg:480
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/quenoth/Youth.cfg:537
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/quenoth/Youth.cfg:594
